# Summary
This documentation page explains Amplitude's "Releases" feature, which tracks product changes as markers on time-series charts, with automated release detection for Growth/Enterprise plans based on semantic versioning and manual creation options for Plus plans, along with detailed reporting capabilities to analyze user response to product changes.

